api_list.description: This method provides you with information regarding the language codes which our code checker supports
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://hackerrank-hackerrank.p.rapidapi.com/https://api.hackerrank.com/checker/languages.json"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "hackerrank-hackerrank.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
